this feature is called virtual desktop
Open the bar and look for 'virtual desktop'
you can then add more desktops as you wish

you can also set shortcut to swtich

the defautl ones are: ctrl+f1, ctrl+f2... etc

you can also set Switch to Next Desktop and to Previous desktop
(set ctrl+win+right / left arrow) and also 'Walk through Desktop List'
(you can set ctrl+ win + tab)

the system will notify you if you will try to overwrite some existing
shortcuts
